snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Tamriel Unlimited - Liberate the Imperial City
snippet.description:
Watch our latest trailer "Liberate the Imperial City" for a first look at the upcoming Imperial City DLC game pack for The Elder Scrolls Online: Tamriel Unlimited, coming to PC/Mac on August 31st, Xbox One on September 15th, and PlayStation 4 on September 16.

For more information about The Elder Scrolls Online: Tamriel Unlimited, visit our website: http://elderscrollsonline.com.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+ElderScrollsOnline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence
